shire (see   Sudbury  ), is also formally possible but no evidence has been found that definitely links the two names. This surname is found in Cornwall from the late 13th century."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sudbury was born about 1340. He married Mrs. Sudbury about 1359. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"about 1340–":"umbes 1340–Surnud","1340–Female":"1340–Surnud","1359–Female":"1359–Surnud","1340–Male":"1340–Surnud","1359":"1359","about 1359":"umbes 1359","1340":"1340","about 1340":"umbes 1340","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fi":{"about 1340–":"noin 1340–Kuollut","1340–Female":"1340–Kuollut","1359–Female":"1359–Kuollut","1340–Male":"1340–Kuollut","1359":"1359","about 1359":"noin 1359","1340":"1340","about 1340":"noin 1340","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fr":{"about 1340–":"environ 1340–Décédé","1340–Female":"1340–Décédée","1359–Female":"1359–Décédée","1340–Male":"1340–Décédé","1359":"1359","about 1359":"environ 1359","1340":"1340","about 1340":"environ 1340","Scotland":"Écosse","lifeSummary":"Sudbury est né environ 1340. Il a épousé Mrs. Sudbury environ 1359. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"about 1340–":"um 1340–Verstorben","1340–Female":"1340–Verstorben","1359–Female":"1359–Verstorben","1340–Male":"1340–Verstorben","1359":"1359","about 1359":"um 1359","1340":"1340","about 1340":"um 1340","Scotland":"Scotland","lifeSummary":"Sudbury wurde um 1340 geboren. Er hat um 1359 Mrs. Sudbury geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"about 1340–":"about 1340–Desede","1340–Female":"1340–Desede","1359–Female":"1359–Desede","1340–Male":"1340–Desede","1359":"1359","about 1359":"about 1359","1340":"1340","about 1340":"about 1340","Scotland":"Scotland"},"hu":{"about 1340–":"1340 körül–elhunyt","1340–Female":"1340–elhunyt","1359–Female":"1359–elhunyt","1340–Male":"1340–elhunyt","1359":"1359","about 1359":"1359 körül","1340":"1340","about 1340":"1340 körül","Scotland":"Scotland"},"id":{"about 1340–":"sekitar 1340–Telah Meninggal","1340–Female":"1340–Telah Meningg